{"tid":1643050,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[有車牌] 新巴職員在紅館外遭襲擊 警方緊急熱線 999 未能接通","createTime":"2019-10-10T03:10:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T03:24:15.000Z","uid":23707,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0c0e2509b0b3ee96db147367edcea0b9e5454e99","tid":1643050,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T03:10:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5HGgSEA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5HGgSEA.png&h=feddb06d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有職員群組流傳：今晚有新巴職員在紅館外指示演唱會觀眾乘車時，被一輛懷疑有黑幫背景的白色寶馬白牌車司機襲擊，有職員分別被推倒在地上及頭部被打，亦有人被恐嚇。職員曾經嘗試致電999報警但無人接聽，結果只能向公司求助<br />\n資料及相片自車長群組<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkitalk.net/HKiTalk2/thread-1147938-1-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkitalk.net%2FHKiTalk2%2Fthread-1147938-1-1.html&d=N3SWmacea4shigR4hA2EmwmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=462477f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkitalk.net/HKiTalk2/thread-1147938-1-1.html</a>"},{"pid":"baf3f32709ae9aaeeb0b187909a093a9ac691791","tid":1643050,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T03:10:26.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n未fc"},{"pid":"0618f4d68bce72c5a1310a5514d90ec59699a023","tid":1643050,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T03:10:51.000Z","msg":"黑警全家不得好死，永不超生！"},{"pid":"f3db7d0c52730d9cb166c9f0c31994bb200ed7b5","tid":1643050,"uid":103668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T03:11:05.000Z","msg":"鶳"},{"pid":"20ba001a09bc7df32069da8150590adc410110d2","tid":1643050,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T03:12:05.000Z","msg":"膠talk有人話今晚都會出現"},{"pid":"bdde33bd47ac13b080f8c849f669a5594fb23743","tid":1643050,"uid":210452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T03:20:40.000Z","msg":"影衰曬渣寶馬既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse